    public class WellDataDetailFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements WellDataDetailView
    A simple Fragment subclass. Activities that contain this fragment must implement the WellDataDetailFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener interface to handle interaction events. Use the newInstance(int, qv21.com.wellconstruction.domain.Owner) factory method to create an instance of this fragment.
